Method.name: %OnDrawHTMLHead
Method.Description:
This callback is called at the end of the HTML HEAD section of the page.
(default implementation is a simple expression).
Method.Implementation:
Write "<meta http-equiv='cache-control' content='no-cache, must-revalidate'>",! Write "<meta http-equiv='expires' content='-1'>",! ;Write "<meta http-equiv='pragma' content='no-cache'>",!
q $$$OK
